WEBVTT

00:01:29.705 --> 00:01:32.176
That I tried to do.

00:01:34.036 --> 00:01:35.847
Friends,

00:01:37.367 --> 00:01:43.370
most of the brightest ideas
came to my mind out of anger.

00:01:43.814 --> 00:01:53.514
Like when I was 35 and sat 
in a locked-up, tiny prison.

00:01:54.564 --> 00:01:57.067
The whole night, I was angry.

00:01:57.957 --> 00:02:01.017
But it has given birth to a new idea.